{"tid":180949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三星fans川普改用iPhone 再掀駭客疑慮熱議","createTime":"2017-03-31T09:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T03:11:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec31b3b029f74010948088d8e8855b586d0a3f2c","tid":180949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"法新社 &ndash; 2小時25分前<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/RlK.YIWnfniTbyeexUA.TA--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztmaT1pbnNldDtoPTQ5NTtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc5O3c9NzY4/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/afp/int0017b.170331143504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRlK.YIWnfniTbyeexUA.TA--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztmaT1pbnNldDtoPTQ5NTtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc5O3c9NzY4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fafp%2Fint0017b.170331143504.jpg&h=bad1e78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（法新社紐約30日電） 美國總統川普有新機了，是一支蘋果iPhone。通常這算不上是新聞。不過，產量豐富的白宮推文有遭駭客攻擊的安全疑慮風險。從這個角度來看，川普換手機就變得超有哏了。 網路安全專家表示，川普將手機從Android系統改成iPhone的決定，在安全上是正面的，但也不代表駭客風險就此煙消雲散。 有關他舊手機的細節從未公開，但據信他原本用的是不安全的舊款三星機。 前美國空軍網路安全官，現在服務於德州顧問公司Denim Group的狄克森（John Dickson）說：「我敢保證，俄羅斯與中國都會試圖摸清楚要怎麼攻擊。」 一些分析師認為蘋果的裝置可能較安全，因為蘋果自行掌控軟、硬體，且不時更新其操作系統。 不過加州大學長期網路安全中心（Center for Long-Term Cybersecurity ）執行長庫柏（Betsy Cooper）說，儘管蘋果有好名聲，但最近的研究顯示「iPhones與Android都難逃駭客毒手」。 針對川普換機一事，蘋果沒有回覆法新社的提問。（譯者：中央社許湘欣）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%94%B9%E7%94%A8iphone-%E5%86%8D%E6%8E%80%E9%A7%AD%E5%AE%A2%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-063504733.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%2594%25A8iphone-%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258E%2580%25E9%25A7%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2585%25AE%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25AD%25B0-063504733.html&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7NWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=2c782c78\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%94%B9%E7%94%A8iphone-%E5%86%8D%E6%8E%80%E9%A7%AD%E5%AE%A2%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-063504733.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c96b97e5f49ad82dfbb7b05128acc9af169d50c","tid":180949,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:10:53.000Z","msg":"身家40億都用舊款手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7884b91e5342f416567a65fc6829af25ce6ac35c","tid":180949,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身家40億都用舊款手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國總統用咩電話唔係自己話事"},{"pid":"9bfdd0312f32508deb62d2efc8df14f10df4c582","tid":180949,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>身家40億都用舊款手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國總統用咩電話唔係自己話事</blockquote><br />\n講緊佢原本嗰部"},{"pid":"cd46c09534cdbcf5bf34cc7cb7a96f2cef352706","tid":180949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T23:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ea692c3865ef00e56979df114fddf4cc81266b","tid":180949,"uid":30845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:57:49.000Z","msg":"Galaxy s3"},{"pid":"5135ec11fcd540d7baf1f0a93312440d614ae3cf","tid":180949,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:17:18.000Z","msg":"blackbarry<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847657d1c8d5acf43447e4dba3b16569336ff533","tid":180949,"uid":16830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身家40億都用舊款手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同誠哥隻手表一樣道理，有好多有錢人唔識佢係街撞到，單睇行頭一定睇唔出係有錢人"},{"pid":"8c0d9d590c50b73ff1647bb0c304e169f7c037b6","tid":180949,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0